  "remarks": "Emerged on 13 Sep. 2014. Most known for its abduction and subsequent beheading\n                of French national Herve Gourdel. Claimed responsibility for attacking police and\n                gendarmes in Algeria and continued planning future attacks. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
